{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "致觀眾", "storyInfo": "蒂比探望在獄中的莫伊拉。《杜邦夫人》的完整版頗具爭議，成為了電影節最受注目的作品。新酒神盧西恩在影院與劇作家和暮落見面，並準備踏上新的旅程。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomC", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>哥倫比亞，藍卡塢郊外，聯邦移動監獄</><p=2>兩個月後</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，你變得好瘦哦！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟在床上躺了兩個月嘛。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時地塊停下來的第一時間我就去找你了。我看到醫護人員抬著你出來，你渾身都是血，一動不動，我以為你已經……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的歌聲……很可怕。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他只是想讓我停下來，並不想真的殺了我。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他絕對不是像格蕾塔說的那樣，在劇本拍賣會上與她偶遇，被說服後跟來劇組的，他另有目的。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另有目的？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在找某個存在，某個就在我們身邊但我們一無所知的存在。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "蒂比", "content": "啊，我本來就覺得盧西恩很神秘，你這樣講我就更一頭霧水了……"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "蒂比", "end": "true", "content": "算了不說他了！", "joined": "啊，我本來就覺得盧西恩很神秘，你這樣講我就更一頭霧水了……算了不說他了！"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的對不起，莫麗，過了這麼久才來看你。主要是、主要是聯邦移動監獄的探視申請有點麻煩……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道的，蒂比。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我利用了你，害你被誤會……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生說的沒錯，我甚至忽略了我本就擁有的真實。在我陷入癲狂的最後時刻，我甚至，沒有想到你……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，你聽我說。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論你經歷了什麼，無論你因為什麼目的，你都傷害了那些和我們朝夕相處的人，你做了無法饒恕的事，我永遠、永遠都不會原諒你！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但是莫麗，這並不影響我懷念我們兩個人窩在沙發裡看恐怖片的那些時光。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼快樂，那麼真實，不是嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是啊。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#12$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "躺在病床上的時候，傷口很痛，睡不著，我就一直在回想這段時間發生的一切……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#12$3"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一整夜過去，只有我自己的疼痛是最真實的。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#12$3"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，無論故事被寫得多麼荒唐，無論我們是不是命運的傀儡，我並不是沒有機會。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們在一起看電影的時候，我能更專心一點，而不是去想那些我以為自己看到的真相、仇恨和瘋狂、鮮血和人偶……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，蒂比。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$3"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我可以早點遇見你的話，或許你就不需要“勞拉”了……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過兩天就是最終的庭審了吧？我諮詢過幾位律師，好像……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$3"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用在意結果，蒂比。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "典獄長人很好，他允許我最後這幾天待在監獄的後勤部門，去做一些犯人們用得到的東西。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不是，像之前那樣，虛妄地等待最後的……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好、那就好。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你探視的時間好像不多了，說點開心的事情吧。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇組拍的那部電影最後怎麼樣了？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$3"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "loop": "true", "channel": "cr", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g1_setting_lobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>哥倫比亞，藍卡塢主城區，“另類電影節”播映現場</><p=2>一天前</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_carpet_normal_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1", "posfrom": "70,0", "posto": "70,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-70,0", "posto": "-70,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，大家都已經在這裡了啊，對不起我遲到了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬，緊張嗎？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一點。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放輕鬆。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後的拍攝以那樣荒唐的方式結束，剪輯、調色、音樂製作……兩個月的時間完成後期製作，每個人都已經盡力了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬，很高興在電影名的修改上，我們達成了共識。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮女士，也感謝您最後在天災中的那段表演。否則，刪掉那兩個字只是我個人內心的自我鬥爭罷了。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#2$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《杜邦夫人》顯然沒有《杜邦夫人之死》那麼有噱頭，電影的宣傳和發行的事情就讓格蕾塔去苦惱吧……但毫無疑問，這是最適合故事的名字。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交給我吧。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "格蕾塔", "content": "我會讓《杜邦夫人》順利上映……"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "格蕾塔", "end": "true", "content": "然後我會去一趟警局，做我該做的事情。", "joined": "我會讓《杜邦夫人》順利上映……然後我會去一趟警局，做我該做的事情。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "loop": "true", "channel": "cr", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸！捏我一下，我沒有看錯吧？", "name": "興奮的記者A"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "捏個屁，快點拍啦！這絕對是明天的頭條！", "name": "興奮的記者B"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“另類電影節”這種有點冷門的藝術影展，竟然能吸引到這麼重量級的嘉賓出席？主辦單位花了多少錢？", "name": "興奮的記者B"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪麗安娜女士已經有幾年沒出現在藍卡塢了？", "name": "興奮的記者A"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#4$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "130,0", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅拉奶奶！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，小蒂比。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#5$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "130,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這套裝扮……唔，讓我猜一下你現在在劇組裡是什麼身分，場記？道具師？特技演員，“傢俱城戰士”那種？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是布景噴畫師啦！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當了半年多了，我還被選進了藍卡塢的拍攝地塊修復團隊呢，上週的事情！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們劇組租借的那個地塊不是已經被天災毀得面目全非了嘛，老大讓我負責它在重建後的設計工作，忙得團團轉……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，看來你終於確定自己要從事什麼了。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#5$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟您說過的，我喜歡電影，我喜歡它的每一個環節、每一個組成部分……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我終於找到自己在其中最喜歡的是什麼了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，還是不打算回去？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，老頭子那邊，您繼續幫我處理一下嘛。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小蒂比，你的爺爺是我曾經在藍卡塢最好的合作夥伴，多年的好朋友，但這並不代表他會在教育小孩的事情裡參考我的意見。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "蒂比", "content": "您就在下次和他喝茶的時候這麼說——"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "蒂比", "end": "true", "content": "咳咳——", "joined": "您就在下次和他喝茶的時候這麼說——咳咳——"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“老傢伙，我們都已經退休了，沒必要管那麼多啦……”", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“你看，小蒂比沒有利用你的任何資源，沒有按照你的規劃去當歷史片導演，不是也在藍卡塢生活得不錯嗎？”", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“未來，說不定藍卡塢一半的拍攝場景都是你孫女繪製的呢！”", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我已經錄下來了，下次直接放給他聽。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#10$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哎呀，雅拉奶奶~", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了好了，再說我這次回哥倫比亞，可能也沒有時間去見你爺爺。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對哦，您之前不是跑到雷姆必拓散心了嗎，這次回來是為了萊茵生命的事情？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別問太多，小蒂比。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "雅拉", "content": "播映會結束後，我還需要去一趟特區，見一下副總統閣下……"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "雅拉", "end": "true", "content": "所以，現在先讓我和老朋友聊聊天吧。", "joined": "播映會結束後，我還需要去一趟特區，見一下副總統閣下……所以，現在先讓我和老朋友聊聊天吧。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，瑪麗安娜。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫我雅拉吧。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "息影幾十年，“瑪麗安娜”這個名字對我來說已經有點陌生了。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，還是要感謝你……雅拉。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道，憑我如今的影響力，確實很難在藍卡塢說上什麼話……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒有你的幫助，“另類電影節”不會在徵選環節已經結束之後，破例允許《杜邦夫人》在電影節上播映。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太客氣了。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我事先還真不知道蒂比這個孩子竟然是……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我願意幫忙，其實和這個孩子沒有什麼關係。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只不過是看了那段在天災中的表演，覺得如果它不能被觀眾看到，實在是太可惜了，所以想要幫助一下老朋友。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，即使《杜邦夫人》在“另類電影節”上提前造勢，可能對電影最後的票房成績也沒有太大的幫助。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮，你比我更清楚，藍卡塢如果是一個真實的人，那絕對沒有比他記性更差、包容心更小的人了……", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他不一定真的能接納一個重回自己懷抱的戀人。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，你們毀壞了一整個地塊，哪怕電影票房大賣，你們收回的錢也不夠支付賠償金。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起碼我這樣去做了，起碼我沒有遺憾。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起考慮這些，我……我更想問你一個問題。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請說。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初，你拍攝《在永夜裡燃燒的晨星》時也遭遇了天災，攝影機記錄下了你與風暴擦肩而過的畫面……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那究竟如你在發布會上所說，是一個意外，還是……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是主動走向前與它對戲的呢？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#9$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮，對現在的你來說，答案是什麼很重要嗎？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈，不重要。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，到最後，還是很難說贏過了你啊！", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盛裝的女主角在媒體的鏡頭前開懷大笑，她也不知道自己笑什麼。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "良久，她朝著曾經的競爭對手，幻想中那個自己永遠追不上的天才，曾經無數次在鏡頭前禮貌地行貼面禮的對象，張開了懷抱……"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們相擁。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "入場吧。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_893_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_tvnoise", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "米蘭妮·盧瑟福德   飾演   杜邦夫人", "delay": 0.001, "width": 800.